query:
UPDATE rentalContracts 
SET contractNumber = CONCAT('CTR-', DATE_FORMAT(createdAt, '%Y%m%d'), '-', LPAD(id, 4, '0'), '-', UNIX_TIMESTAMP(createdAt));
